high_descs: Turn right and go straight, then go to the microwave, then turn left and go to the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug on the counter, to the right of the coffee maker.
Turn left, go straight, then turn right to go to the white fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Turn around, go left, then turn left at the the coffee maker.
Place the mug at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold mug at the coffee maker.

high_descs: Stand in front of the coffee maker you see in front of you.
Get the mug you see to the right of the coffee maker.
Turn left and walk almost to the table then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Cool the mug in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Walk back to the coffee maker.
Put the mug under the coffee makers spout.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold coffee mug under the coffee makers spout.

high_descs: Move to the right and stand at the counter in front of the coffee maker.
Pick the cup up off of the counter.
Go left and stand in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the cup inside, close the fridge and then open it and take the cup out.
Turn around and go stand in front of the coffee maker on the counter.
Put the cup under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled cup under a coffee maker.
